                status: 0,
                msg: 'nano connect is fail in ssr player_connect' + e
            }
          }
        }
      </script></div> <div data-v-02ce7bab><script type="text/javascript">

        if (document.querySelector('.bpx-docker')){
          if (window['NanoInitStage']){
            window['NanoInitStage']['SSR_DOMDetect'] ={
              status: 1,
              msg:'SSR succeed to detect Dom'
            }
          }
        }
        else{
          if (window['NanoInitStage']){
            window['NanoInitStage']['SSR_DOMDetect'] ={
              status: 0,
              msg:'SSR failed to detect Dom'
            }
